      Our team identifies apartments and developments with strong market demand, high rental yield, 
      and appreciation potential.
    </p>

    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1.5rem;">
      <div style="border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 1rem;">
        <img src="/images/apartment1.jpg" alt="Modern Apartment" style="width: 100%; border-radius: 6px;" />
