      <div style="border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 1rem;">
        <img src="/images/beach-apartment.jpg" alt="Beachside Apartment" style="width: 100%; border-radius: 6px;" />
        <h3>Beachside Property ‚Äì Portugal</h3>
        <p>Price: $310,000 | Estimated Return: 10% annually</p>
        <a href="/contact-info" style="color: #0070f3; font-weight: bold;">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr style="margin: 3rem 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #ccc;" />

    <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem;">üí∞ Cryptocurrency Opportunities</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      We analyze crypto projects and digital assets using deep data insights. 
      Each opportunity is rated based on risk, growth potential, and liquidity ‚Äî 
      helping you make smarter decisions in a fast-changing market.
